sentences.sentence: Liana: I hope you can do the same with the new assignment too.

sentences.sentence: Liana stood on the doorway silently. She just came round to realise what had happened.
sentences.translation: 莉安娜静静地站在门口。她这才恍然觉悟到底发生了什么事。

sentences.sentence: Liana was the main media and connection through which hoolock gibbon traveled between arbor forests and shrubs.
